<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Set up just like any AE group, except you may want a tank for break in. Or being so highly gear you can probably tank there without problem when you do break in.
<br />

<br />
2-3 enchanters for ae stun ( amy may have higher resist rate than other stuff, but with 3 chanters chain stunning you should do ok)
<br />

<br />
1 cleric ofcouse ( cleric got AE too + they heal!) 
<br />

<br />
2-3 wiz/mag/druid for ae nukeage, take mage or druid if you can't find wiz
<br />

<br />
Once you are in, just move to fire wall and have an AEr pull something from temple, you will get atleast 95% of the temple there should be atleast 1 whip drop <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="icon_biggrin.gif" border="0" />
<br />
NEVER mess with the imps.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
