<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Chain WoM and Stun. The repop times on them are pretty solid for chaining. A note about the Imp (Not sure if they changed it or not.) But he is(was) a social mob. So if he pops from a corpse while you're aeing, expect to be attacked. Best bet is to kill a few at a time and leave imps alone if you can. Or atleast kill last. If he should happen to pop, just have a bard train him away with FM. He doesn't move from the spot. But I'd agree 100% about bard for breakin. All he has to do is run in circles until everyone gets in zone and situated, then FM and start the pulls. Really easy nowadays. And ofcourse, you'll get to see his name randomly spammed in shouts as he gets DTed(If golems are up). So all get a good laugh.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
